Subject: [PATCH] patch 0875+0876: turnaround + USA analytics actionability
 rewrite

- Turnaround: default to TURNAROUNDS-ONLY view, context banner with dataset
  mix, view toggle, stats strip 10->6, data-missing coaching on empty panels
- USA: stats strip 10->6 with subtitles, new TOP BUYS shortlist
  (A+/A x R40>=40 x Piotroski>=6 x clean forensics x earnings>7d), new
  AT-RISK ROWS list (sorted by score), sector exposure 8->5, R40 buckets
  6->4 (FAIL/PASS/STRONG/ELITE), leaderboard 15->10
